metadata.name: TIMEWRECKED #1
metadata.description: Every studio has a beginning, and this is ours. With web3 on the rise, we are on the verge of a gold rush era. We are walking the grounds, and noticing glimmers of gold dust under our feet. You have to buy the land to get the gold, and with Timewrecked, that is exactly what you would be doing. Nexthollywood is a decentralized movie studio, we are pioneers and one of the leaders in the web3-film space. Our team is composed of both film industry natives and web 3 natives. Through community efforts and support we can build a decentralized studio that gives opportunity for filmmakers, storty-tellers and artists to have their films made without a studio breathing down their back.
